Task Edit Frontend
Edit task by showing previous new task form with previous task data without subtasks card

call function post with arguments:
	identifier from constants.js file (IDENTIFIERS.TASKS.EDIT_TASK), 
	taskDataObject,
	& success & failed callbacks
success callback will call notifyResult then close edit form.
failed will call notifyResult with messege = data.userMsg then close form

post (IDENTIFIERS.TASKS.EDIT_TASK, taskData, success(){}, failed(data){});

in master branch: "public/constants.js" you will find the identifier & steps for this post call

